exercises.name: Incline DB Press 45 Degree

warmupSets.notes: around the world, lift ass off the bench or let the shoulders drop to extreme range of motion under load, keep breathing, rep count feeling based
unilateral with rotation, massage the shoulder ball and socket joint by rotating elbows all around at bottom position, rep count feeling based
unilateral without rotation, can go explosive and controlled descent or play with more time under tension with very slow reps to feel deepest muscles.
